INSERT INTO job_descriptions (title, description, responsibilities, qualifications, salaryRangeMin, salaryRangeMax, currency, employmentType, departmentId, reportsTo, createdAt, updatedAt) VALUES 
('Software Engineer', 'Develop and maintain software applications', 'Write clean code, participate in code reviews, collaborate with team members, debug and fix issues', 'Bachelor degree in CS or related field, 2+ years experience, proficiency in JavaScript/TypeScript', '50000', '80000', 'BDT', 'full_time', 1, 'Engineering Manager', NOW(), NOW()),
('Sales Executive', 'Drive sales and business development', 'Identify prospects, conduct presentations, negotiate contracts, achieve sales targets', 'Bachelor degree, 1+ years sales experience, excellent communication skills', '40000', '70000', 'BDT', 'full_time', 2, 'Sales Manager', NOW(), NOW()),
('HR Coordinator', 'Support HR operations and employee relations', 'Manage recruitment, handle employee queries, maintain HR records, organize training', 'Bachelor in HR or related field, 1+ years HR experience, knowledge of labor laws', '35000', '55000', 'BDT', 'full_time', 3, 'HR Manager', NOW(), NOW()),
('Operations Manager', 'Oversee daily business operations', 'Manage processes, optimize efficiency, coordinate teams, ensure quality standards', 'Bachelor degree, 3+ years operations experience, leadership skills', '60000', '100000', 'BDT', 'full_time', 4, 'Director', NOW(), NOW()),
('Finance Analyst', 'Analyze financial data and prepare reports', 'Prepare budgets, analyze financial statements, forecast trends, support decision making', 'Bachelor in Finance/Accounting, 2+ years experience, proficiency in Excel', '45000', '75000', 'BDT', 'full_time', 5, 'Finance Manager', NOW(), NOW());
